short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension optimizes daily work when adding freight - it automatically sends orders for cargo transportation.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Presenting a new and improved version of the famous extension Freight Assistant 4.0! The main difference of the new extension is speed, now the exchange of your offers with your favorite transport exchanges will be even faster. Place orders, look for free loads without wasting time duplicating information.


**Added language localization - Hungarian became available automatically.
***4.2.7. Added request notification.
****4.2.11 fixed bug for search loads
*****4.2.12 fixed minor bugs
*****4.3.3 add search transport offer
4.39. fixed search bugs
4.3.10 added czech language
